         <abstract id="aspace_f052f8658caeaeae2848320b75c93ccb">The papers include correspondence and legal documents relating to the careers of Lewis Atterbury (d. 1693), Lewis Atterbury (1656-1731), and Francis Atterbury, as well as various receipts, epitaphs, poems, prayers, and seals.</abstract>
    
      </did>
